Best Time to Visit: October to February (Winter season) is the most pleasant time to visit Warangal when the weather is cooler and more enjoyable. <br>

Ideal Vacation Duration: 2-3 days <br>

Average expenses: Starting from ₹25,000 (3 days/2 nights) <br>
Things to Do: <br>

Explore the Warangal Fort complex and learn about the region's history. <br>
Visit the temples and experience the spiritual and architectural significance. <br>
Spend time at the Kakatiya Rock Garden and enjoy the sculptures and lush greenery. <br>

Places to Visit: <br>

Warangal Fort: A massive historical fort with impressive stone gateways, ruins, and gardens. <br>
Thousand Pillar Temple: An ancient temple known for its exquisite architecture and numerous pillars. <br>
Bhadrakali Temple: A renowned Hindu temple dedicated to Goddess Bhadrakali. <br>




